description: Deletes an SageMaker experiment. All trials associated with the experiment must be deleted first. Use the ListTrials API to get a list of the trials associated with the experiment.

parameters.name: ExperimentName
parameters.description: The name of the experiment to delete.

nested_items.name: ExperimentArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the experiment that is being deleted.
